    template: `
    <lai-clean-layout>
      <lai-clean-layout-left [background]="backgroundImage" [title]="title">
        <lai-body level="sm" style="color: white">

variables.defaultValue:
{
  args,
  render: props => ({
    props,
    template: `
      <lai-tab-group [size]="size"
                     [type]="type"
                     (selectedChange)="selectedChange($event)">
        <lai-tab *ngFor="let item of data; let last = last"
                 [label]="item.label"
                 [disabled]="last">
          {{ item.content }}
        </lai-tab>
      </lai-tab-group>
    `,
  }),
}
